uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.core

Interface PAATEval_

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OXPathCache

    public interface PAATEval_
extends OXPathCache
    Interface used to wrap the eval_ visitor so that the OXPathMemoizer can be used with it. The resulting proxy objects handle memoization and we can just solve and abstract the memoization
    Author:
    AndrewJSel, Giovanni Grasso
